{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think it must have been already towards the end of the war or whatever-- I guess the end of '43, somewhere along there, or maybe the beginning of '44, because there was a lot of bombardment going on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was, like, hiding there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To me, it seemed like it was all night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if it was all night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It could have been just an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I just remember, you know, the bombs, and-- and the artillery, and flashes, and just being hidden under this blanket with the rats and-- all over, and just really not knowing if my mother was gonna get back.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, what if she was caught?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And just thinking over and over, what will I do if she doesn't come back?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where am I going to go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What should I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Will I remember how to go back to this other place?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And just all night, going over and over, and just thinking of what will happen if she doesn't come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Do you remember your feelings when she does come back to you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, she was my whole security.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But sometimes when I think that at that point-- I was, like, maybe six years old-- and, you know, when I had my own children, I thought about it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, how can a six-year-old think in terms of trying to make a plan to run away, to actually be able to go somewhere and hide and do all of that?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I just can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember thinking that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She dug up some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess it was gold coins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it 5's.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what it means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a fifth or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
